c: 16
v: 115
t: "Iye wakuletsani kudya zinthu zofa zokha, liwende, nyama ya nkhumba, ndiponso nyama iliyonse imene yaphedwa m’dzina la mulungu wina wosati Mulungu mmodzi yekha. Koma ngati wina akakamizidwa kudya zina za izi, osati mofuna yekha kapena mofuna kuphwanya malamulo, ndithudi, Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi wachifundo chosatha"